Dataset Exploration
  Work Done: Explored dataset using pandas (df.info(), df.describe()) and visualized spam/ham distribution with seaborn.
Why/How: Helps understand class imbalance (important for ML).
Learned: Visualization gives insights into dataset characteristics.
Code Example:
import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
df = pd.read_csv('spam.csv', encoding='latin-1')[['v1','v2']]
df.columns = ['label', 'text']
sns.countplot(x='label', data=df)
